OL,3,CFormer mounted police officers charged
OL,4,Cwith child rape
OL,6,FFormer sergeant William Baker, 78, has
OL,7,Fbeen charged with three counts of
OL,8,Findecent assault and two counts of
OL,9,Frape against a girl under the age of
OL,10,F16.
OL,12,FFormer PC Ian Hopkinson, 63, has been
OL,13,Fcharged with five counts of indecent
OL,14,Fassault and five counts of rape of the
OL,15,Fsame girl.
OL,17,FA woman came forward in 2023 and
OL,18,Freported being the victim of serious
OL,19,Fsexual offences and both men were
OL,20,Farrested on 27 June 2024.
